Question: In at least one image there are two llamas.

Reference Answer: True

Left image URL: https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-s/0c/34/f8/ed/awana-kancha.jpg

Right image URL: https://i.ytimg.com/vi/YNwHdMkmMM8/maxresdefault.jpg

Program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many llamas are in the image?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many llamas are in the image?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} == 2 or {ANSWER1} == 2')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
